Class ArrayDataArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • lexa.core.data.BaseDataArray
      • lexa.core.data.ArrayDataArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<DataArray>, java.lang.Iterable<DataValue>, DataArray, DataFactoryItem

    public class ArrayDataArray
extends BaseDataArray
    An array of values The array is self sizing, as it is implemented as a linked list. The values are polymorphic as they are always held as DataValue objects.
